vht.name: usertype.vht
vht.description: Community health worker responsible for providing primary health care services at the community level.

public_health_officer.name: usertype.public-health-officer
public_health_officer.description: Professional responsible for public health-related activities.

health_coordinator.name: usertype.health-coordinator
health_coordinator.description: Coordinator responsible for managing and coordinating health initiatives.

program_manager.name: usertype.program-manager
program_manager.description: Manager responsible for overseeing health programs.

health_advisor.name: usertype.health-advisor
health_advisor.description: Advisor providing guidance and expertise in the field of health.

public_health_advisor.name: usertype.public-health-advisor
public_health_advisor.description: Advisor providing guidance and expertise in public health-related matters.

unchr.name: usertype.unchr
unchr.description: United Nations High Commissioner for Refugees involved in providing assistance and support to refugees and displaced persons.

ministry_of_health.name: usertype.ministry-of-health
ministry_of_health.description: Government ministry responsible for overseeing health services and programs at the national level.

reported_date_format: ddd, MMM Do, YYYY [at] h:mm A

purge.fn: function(userCtx, contact, reports, messages, chtScriptApi, permissions) { const old = Date.now() - (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24 * 365); return reports.filter(r => r.reported_date < old).map(r => r._id);}
